children.name: Rules
children.text:
A handheld cylinder with an adjustable lens resembling a mechanical eye. 
While a sunshard is inside of it, when you expend a charge from the sunshard to cast light (a normal property of sunshards), you can choose for the light to be shaped like a cone or line instead of a radius. Regardless of the shape, it still creates 20 feet of bright light followed by 20 feet of dim light.
